<template>
  <navbar
    :pages="pages"
    :activePage="activePage"
    :nav-link-click="(index) => activePage = index"
  ></navbar>

  <page-viewer
    :page="pages[activePage]"
  ></page-viewer>


</template>

<script>
import PageViewer from '../../vue-oving-spa/src/components/PageViewer.vue'
import Navbar from '../../vue-oving-spa/src/components/Navbar.vue'

export default {
  components: {
    Navbar,
    PageViewer
  },
  created() {
    this.getPages()
  },
  data () {
    return {
      activePage: 0,
      pages: [
        {
          link: { text: 'Home', url: 'index.html' },
          pageTitle: 'Home Page',
          content: 'This is the home page content'
        },
        {
          link: { text: 'Calculator', url: 'services.html' },
          pageTitle: 'Calculator Page',
          content: 'This is the calculator page content'},
        {
          link: { text: 'About', url: 'about.html' },
          pageTitle: 'About Page',
          content: 'This is the about page content'
        },
        {
          link: { text: 'Contact', url: 'contact.html' },
          pageTitle: 'Contact Page',
          content: 'This is the contact page content'
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  methods: {
    async getPages() {
      let res = await fetch('pages.json')
      let data = await res.json()
    }
  }
}
</script>
